WEBVTT

00:01.435 --> 00:02.703
(male announcer)
IN THE CRIMINAL JUSTICE SYSTEM,

00:02.736 --> 00:05.739
SEXUALLY BASED OFFENSES ARE
CONSIDERED ESPECIALLY HEINOUS.

00:05.773 --> 00:08.476
IN NEW YORK CITY,
THE DEDICATED DETECTIVES

00:08.509 --> 00:10.344
WHO INVESTIGATE
THESE VICIOUS FELONIES

00:10.378 --> 00:11.712
ARE MEMBERS
OF AN ELITE SQUAD

00:11.745 --> 00:13.747
KNOWN AS
THE SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT.

00:13.781 --> 00:15.783
THESE ARE THEIR STORIES.

00:15.816 --> 00:17.485
[alarm ringing]

00:17.518 --> 00:19.420
(Peege)
PHONE ALARM, BOX NUMBER 3354,

00:19.453 --> 00:21.322
1629 BROADWAY.

00:21.355 --> 00:23.624
STRUCTURAL FIRE
IN A BROWNSTONE.

00:23.657 --> 00:25.093
[alarms]

00:25.126 --> 00:28.096
(Gezmur)
DISPATCH,
ENGINE 99 IS EN ROUTE.

00:28.129 --> 00:30.098
(fire truck driver)
HOLD ON!

00:30.131 --> 00:32.666
GET THAT CAB OUTTA HERE!

00:32.700 --> 00:34.168
(Gezmur)
WHAT THE HELL?

00:34.202 --> 00:35.836
ARE YOU TRYING
TO GET YOURSELF KILLED?

00:35.869 --> 00:37.771
THE BABY, THE BABY!
WHAT'S WRONG?

00:37.805 --> 00:39.707
SHE'S SICK!
WHERE'D YOU FIND HER?

00:39.740 --> 00:41.542
A LADY LEFT HER
IN MY TAXI.

00:41.575 --> 00:43.811
THEY SAY BRING BABIES
TO THE FIREHOUSE.

00:43.844 --> 00:45.113
KID'S BURNING UP
WITH THE FEVER, LOU.

00:45.146 --> 00:46.814
MOVE THE CAB.
WE'LL TAKE CARE OF HER.

00:46.847 --> 00:48.616
ENGINE 99 TO DISPATCH.

00:48.649 --> 00:50.684
MEDICAL EMERGENCY
IN FRONT OF QUARTERS.

00:50.718 --> 00:52.386
PLEASE RUSH EMS.

00:52.420 --> 00:54.322
[alarms blaring]

00:55.556 --> 00:57.491
BABY HAS SEVERE
ORAL CANDIDIASIS

00:57.525 --> 00:59.460
AND A TEMP OF 105.

00:59.493 --> 01:01.762
I'D SAY BASED ON HER SIZE,
SHE'S ABOUT FIVE MONTHS.

01:01.795 --> 01:03.097
(Stabler)
YOU LOST ME AT CANDIDIASIS.

01:03.131 --> 01:05.766
(Dr. Massey)
IT'S A FUNGAL INFECTION
COMMONLY KNOWN AS THRUSH.

01:05.799 --> 01:07.235
THAT'S NOT
AN STD, DR. MASSEY.

01:07.268 --> 01:08.736
YEAH, WELL,
SHE WASN'T SEXUALLY ABUSED.

01:08.769 --> 01:10.804
SO WHY'D YOU CALL US?
ACS HANDLES ABANDONED KIDS.

01:10.838 --> 01:13.107
(Dr. Massey)
WHAT'S HAPPENED
TO HER IS A CRIME.

01:13.141 --> 01:15.109
KIDS ONLY GET THIS SICK
WHEN THEY'RE NOT TREATED.

01:15.143 --> 01:16.410
TREATED FOR WHAT?
HIV.

01:16.444 --> 01:18.779
SHE HAS AIDS.
ADVANCED.

01:18.812 --> 01:21.449
AND HER PARENTS DIDN'T DO
A DAMN THING ABOUT IT.

01:21.482 --> 01:23.751
IF THAT'S NOT A CRIME,
WHAT IS?

02:18.739 --> 02:20.241
WHERE DID YOU
DROP HER OFF?

02:20.274 --> 02:22.176
PORT AUTHORITY. SHE LEFT
THE BAG ON THE BACKSEAT.

02:22.210 --> 02:24.245
I NOTICED IT A BLOCK AWAY
WHEN THE BABY STARTED TO CRY.

02:24.278 --> 02:26.414
WHEN I TRIED TO CALM HER,
I FELT THE FEVER.

02:26.447 --> 02:28.349
(Morales)
CAB-CAM TAKES TEN IMAGES,

02:28.382 --> 02:30.584
ONE PER SECOND
AFTER DOOR OPENS OR CLOSES.

02:30.618 --> 02:33.521
HERE'S THE LAST PHOTO.

02:33.554 --> 02:34.688
9:43 A.M.

02:34.722 --> 02:36.224
(Stabler)
MARONG AT THE FIREHOUSE.

02:36.257 --> 02:39.693
BABY'S MOTHER SHOULD BE
RIGHT BEFORE THIS.

02:39.727 --> 02:43.731
(Morales)
NOT UNLESS SHE'S
A 65-YEAR-OLD MAN.

02:43.764 --> 02:46.200
HE'S THE NEXT FACE
BACK IN THE CAMERA'S MEMORY.

02:48.236 --> 02:50.304
(Stabler)
MR. MARONG!
COME HERE.

02:52.873 --> 02:54.508
MR. MARONG,

02:54.542 --> 02:58.246
THE BABY'S MOTHER
WASN'T ON THAT CAMERA.

02:58.279 --> 02:59.980
HOW COULD THAT BE?

03:00.013 --> 03:02.383
'CAUSE THERE IS NO MOTHER?

03:02.416 --> 03:05.986
I WANT YOU TO TELL ME
WHAT REALLY HAPPENED.

03:06.019 --> 03:08.356
I TURN OFF THE CAMERA
BEFORE THE LADY GOT IN MY CAR.

03:08.389 --> 03:09.790
AND YOU DIDN'T RUN THE METER

03:09.823 --> 03:12.360
BECAUSE YOU WANTED TO PUT A FEW
EXTRA BUCKS IN YOUR POCKET?

03:12.393 --> 03:13.227
GAS COST SO MUCH.

03:13.261 --> 03:15.963
IT'S THE ONLY WAY
TO MAKE ENDS MEET.

03:15.996 --> 03:19.333
I TURN OFF THE CAMERA IN CASE
THE TAXI COMMISSIONER CHECKS IT.

03:19.367 --> 03:21.001
(Benson)
EL.

03:21.034 --> 03:22.770
STAY RIGHT HERE.

03:22.803 --> 03:24.738
THAT WAS MUNCH.
HE RAN MARONG--NO RECORD.

03:24.772 --> 03:26.474
AND NO BABY GIRLS
WENT MISSING

03:26.507 --> 03:29.277
IN THE LAST MONTH
IN THE TRI-STATE AREA.

03:29.310 --> 03:31.279
THAT'S GREAT.
HE TURNED OFF THE CAB-CAM.

03:31.312 --> 03:33.481
NO PICTURES
OF THE BABY'S MOTHER.
[cell phone rings]

03:33.514 --> 03:34.548
OKAY.

03:34.582 --> 03:37.851
MR. MARONG, WE'RE SENDING YOU
OVER TO OUR OFFICE

03:37.885 --> 03:40.388
SO YOU CAN DESCRIBE THE BABY'S
MOTHER TO A SKETCH ARTIST.

03:40.421 --> 03:42.390
I'LL DO MY BEST.

03:43.591 --> 03:46.294
WARNER NEEDS US
AT THE MORGUE.

03:48.028 --> 03:49.463
DID THE BABY DIE?

03:49.497 --> 03:50.798
NO, BUT SHE'S SEPTIC.

03:50.831 --> 03:54.602
DR. MASSEY'S LOADING HER UP
WITH BIG GUN ANTIBIOTICS.

03:54.635 --> 03:56.937
SO WHY ARE YOU INVOLVED WITH
A KID WHO'S STILL BREATHING?

03:56.970 --> 03:58.372
MASSEY AND I WORKED
TOGETHER

03:58.406 --> 03:59.940
ON AN AIDS
SURVEILLANCE TEAM.

03:59.973 --> 04:01.875
SHE SENT ME AN ORAL SWAB
FROM YOUR BABY DOE

04:01.909 --> 04:03.611
SO I COULD RUN HER DNA.

04:03.644 --> 04:05.613
WHY? SHE'S NOT GONNA BE
IN THE SYSTEM.

04:05.646 --> 04:07.348
I THOUGHT HER MOTHER
MIGHT BE,

04:07.381 --> 04:09.550
AND THEIR MITOCHONDRIAL DNA
WILL MATCH.

04:09.583 --> 04:11.051
A LOT OF KIDS WITH HIV

04:11.084 --> 04:13.321
ARE BORN TO WOMEN
WITH CRIMINAL RECORDS.

04:13.354 --> 04:15.289
JUNKIES AND HOOKERS.
SO YOU GOT A HIT?

04:15.323 --> 04:17.491
MOM IS JOANNE SUAREZ.

04:17.525 --> 04:19.993
A FREQUENT GUEST OF
THE DEPARTMENT OF CORRECTIONS.

04:20.027 --> 04:21.829
JOANNE HAVE A LAST
KNOWN ADDRESS?

04:21.862 --> 04:24.765
CHARMING LITTLE PLACE.
RIKERS.

04:24.798 --> 04:26.600
[pounds table]
YOU GOT THE WRONG CONVICT.

04:26.634 --> 04:29.403
I DON'T HAVE A DAUGHTER.
CHECK MY INTAKE FORMS.

04:29.437 --> 04:30.738
C.O.!

04:30.771 --> 04:32.606
YEAH, WELL, WE CHECKED
YOUR BABY'S DNA,

04:32.640 --> 04:35.543
AND IT MATCHES YOURS,
SO WHY DON'T YOU SIT DOWN?

04:37.411 --> 04:38.712
WHY'D YOU LIE
TO CORRECTIONS

04:38.746 --> 04:40.514
AND SAY THAT YOU
DIDN'T HAVE A CHILD?

04:40.548 --> 04:43.951
BECAUSE I DIDN'T WANT SOCIAL
SERVICES TO FIND OUT ABOUT HER.

04:43.984 --> 04:45.986
THEY TAKE YOUR BABY
WHEN YOU'RE HIGH.

04:46.019 --> 04:48.489
SO I HAD HER AT HOME.
NEVER GOT A BIRTH CERTIFICATE.

04:48.522 --> 04:50.524
YOU TELL THE FATHER?

04:50.558 --> 04:52.059
I DON'T KNOW WHO HE IS.

04:52.092 --> 04:53.594
SHE'S A TRICK BABY,

04:53.627 --> 04:55.529
BUT THAT DOESN'T MEAN
THAT I DON'T LOVE HER.

04:55.563 --> 04:57.531
WHY ARE YOU HERE?
IS ANTONIA OKAY?

04:57.565 --> 05:00.067
WELL, SHE'S IN THE HOSPITAL
WITH AIDS.

05:01.435 --> 05:03.637
WHICH MEANS
YOU'RE HIV POSITIVE.

05:06.607 --> 05:09.543
BUT I QUIT USING
WHEN I WAS PREGNANT.

05:11.545 --> 05:14.114
I DID EVERYTHING I COULD
TO KEEP HER CLEAN!

05:14.147 --> 05:16.550
EXCEPT TAKING ANTIRETROVIRALS
BEFORE SHE WAS BORN.

05:16.584 --> 05:18.486
WHICH COULD HAVE PREVENTED THIS
FROM HAPPENING.

05:18.519 --> 05:19.787
I NEVER MEANT TO HURT
MY LITTLE GIRL!

05:19.820 --> 05:21.389
WHO'D YOU LEAVE
YOUR CHILD WITH

05:21.422 --> 05:22.690
WHEN YOU GOT LOCKED UP?

05:22.723 --> 05:25.459
[sobs]
IDA JALLOW.

05:25.493 --> 05:26.860
MY DOWNSTAIRS NEIGHBOR.

05:26.894 --> 05:29.730
SHE PROMISED THAT SHE
WOULD TAKE CARE OF HER FOR ME.

05:32.633 --> 05:33.834
(Benson)
IDA JALLOW?

05:33.867 --> 05:34.968
POLICE?

05:35.002 --> 05:36.770
WHAT'S THIS ABOUT?

05:36.804 --> 05:38.706
THERE ARE HERE
TO SEE ME, IDA.

05:38.739 --> 05:40.574
DETECTIVES.

05:40.608 --> 05:43.711
YOU HAVE MORE QUESTIONS.

05:43.744 --> 05:45.613
OUR GREEN CARDS
HAVE EXPIRED.

05:45.646 --> 05:47.881
WE WERE AFRAID WE WOULD BE SENT
BACK TO GAMBIA.

05:47.915 --> 05:49.650
WE DIDN'T KNOW
WHAT TO DO.

05:49.683 --> 05:51.719
ANTONIA JUST GOT
SICKER AND SICKER.

05:51.752 --> 05:54.154
SO YOU LIED ABOUT FINDING HER
IN THE CAB TO GET RID OF HER.

05:54.187 --> 05:56.990
NO! I DIDN'T WANT HER
TO DIE.

05:57.024 --> 05:59.460
WE LOVED HER
LIKE SHE WAS OUR OWN.

05:59.493 --> 06:02.630
EVERYTHING WAS FINE
UNTIL SHE STOPPED EATING.

06:02.663 --> 06:04.465
WE THOUGHT SHE MISSED
HER MOTHER,

06:04.498 --> 06:06.900
THEN I SAW THE WHITE SPOTS
IN HER MOUTH,

06:06.934 --> 06:08.869
AND I KNEW IT WAS AIDS.

06:08.902 --> 06:10.871
HOW?

06:10.904 --> 06:12.640
MANY PEOPLE HAVE DIED
IN MY COUNTRY.

06:12.673 --> 06:15.075
I RAISED MY SISTER,
AND SHE HAD THE SAME SICKNESS.

06:15.108 --> 06:16.710
SO YOU KNEW HOW SICK
ANTONIA WAS.

06:16.744 --> 06:18.412
WHY DIDN'T YOU BRING HER
TO THE HOSPITAL?

06:18.446 --> 06:20.881
BECAUSE THE AIDS MEDICINES
ARE POISON.

06:23.951 --> 06:25.853
WHO TOLD YOU THAT?

06:25.886 --> 06:29.790
OUR PRESIDENT.
BUT HE HAS FOUND A CURE.

06:29.823 --> 06:32.860
HE RUBS A GREEN PASTE OF HERBS
ON HIS PATIENTS' CHESTS--

06:32.893 --> 06:34.161
HOLD ON.

06:34.194 --> 06:37.598
THE PRESIDENT OF GAMBIA
DOES THIS HIMSELF?

06:37.631 --> 06:39.567
EVERY THURSDAY.

06:39.600 --> 06:41.669
AND THEN HE GIVES THEM
THE BITTER YELLOW BREW

06:41.702 --> 06:43.003
AND TWO BANANAS...

06:43.036 --> 06:44.605
AND THEY'RE CURED.

06:44.638 --> 06:47.675
DID YOU TRY TO CURE
ANTONIA?

06:47.708 --> 06:49.743
NO. THE PRESIDENT'S RECIPE
IS SECRET.

06:49.777 --> 06:51.779
(Ida)
SO WE WENT ON THE INTERNET

06:51.812 --> 06:53.514
AND FOUND A DOCTOR
WHO BELIEVES AS WE DO.

06:53.547 --> 06:55.449
HE GAVE ANTONIA VITAMINS.

06:55.483 --> 06:58.018
BUT SHE JUST GOT WORSE.

06:58.051 --> 07:00.654
OKAY. THIS DOCTOR,
WHAT'S HIS NAME?

07:04.625 --> 07:06.660
I ALSO INSTRUCTED
THE MARONGS

07:06.694 --> 07:08.195
TO GIVE HER YOGURT.

07:08.228 --> 07:11.465
YOGURT FOR AIDS.
ARE YOU OUT OF YOUR MIND?

07:11.499 --> 07:14.101
NOT EVERY PATIENT WITH HIV
NEEDS MEDICATION.

07:14.134 --> 07:18.138
ANTONIA SUAREZ PRESENTED
WITH A MINOR CASE OF THRUSH,

07:18.171 --> 07:20.608
AND I CHOSE
AN ALTERNATIVE TREATMENT

07:20.641 --> 07:22.543
WHICH HAS WORKED VERY WELL.

07:22.576 --> 07:23.944
WELL ENOUGH
THAT SHE NEARLY DIED FROM IT.

07:23.977 --> 07:27.481
AND THEN, AS I INSTRUCTED
THE MARONGS,

07:27.515 --> 07:30.684
THEY SHOULD HAVE COME BACK
FOR MORE THERAPY.

07:30.718 --> 07:32.152
LIKE WHAT, PUDDING?

07:32.185 --> 07:35.088
NO, ANTIFUNGAL MEDICATION,

07:35.122 --> 07:37.658
AS ANY MEDICAL PROFESSIONAL
WOULD PRESCRIBE.

07:37.691 --> 07:38.792
A MEDICAL PROFESSIONAL

07:38.826 --> 07:41.562
WOULD HAVE GIVEN THE CHILD
ITS HIV POSITIVE MEDICINE

07:41.595 --> 07:42.596
ON THE FIRST VISIT.

07:42.630 --> 07:43.697
YOU'RE A QUACK.

07:43.731 --> 07:45.666
WE'RE THROUGH.

07:45.699 --> 07:48.669
HOW MANY PEOPLE HAVE YOU CURED
WITH VITAMINS AND YOGURT?

07:48.702 --> 07:50.538
I HAVE PATIENTS WAITING.

07:50.571 --> 07:51.672
GOD HELP THEM.

07:53.641 --> 07:54.975
(Greylek)
HUTTON'S
A WALKING MALPRACTICE SUIT.

07:55.008 --> 07:56.343
STICK THE STATE MEDICAL BOARD
ON HIM.

07:56.376 --> 07:58.879
WHILE MORE OF HIS
PATIENTS DIE?
YOGURT'S NOT A MURDER WEAPON.

07:58.912 --> 08:01.148
HOLISTIC MEDICINE
HAS A PLACE IN THE LAW,

08:01.181 --> 08:03.050
AND PATIENTS HAVE A RIGHT
TO CHOOSE THEIR OWN TREATMENT.

08:03.083 --> 08:05.118
WHEN IT'S BASED ON SCIENCE
AND NOT VOODOO.

08:05.152 --> 08:06.654
WANNA SEE SOME HOCUS-POCUS?

08:06.687 --> 08:09.723
CHECK OUT DR. DEMENTO'S
WEB SITE.

08:09.757 --> 08:11.759
"THE TRUTH ABOUT HIV."

08:11.792 --> 08:13.160
"THERE'S NO PROOF
THAT HIV CAUSES AIDS.

08:13.193 --> 08:14.628
"THE ANTI-HIV MEDICATIONS

08:14.662 --> 08:16.930
BIG PHARMA MAKES
WILL KILL YOU."

08:16.964 --> 08:19.667
THIS GUY
IS A FRUITCAKE.

08:19.700 --> 08:21.702
ACCORDING TO HUTTON,
AIDS IS A GLOBAL CONSPIRACY

08:21.735 --> 08:24.738
FUNDED BY PHARMACEUTICAL
COMPANIES TO MAKE BIG BUCKS.

08:24.772 --> 08:25.873
AND COMMIT GENOCIDE.

08:25.906 --> 08:26.940
MY PARENTS
BELIEVED THE GOVERNMENT

08:26.974 --> 08:28.809
CREATED HIV IN A LAB,

08:28.842 --> 08:32.646
AND THE CIA SPREAD IT IN THE
PRISONS TO KILL BLACKS AND GAYS.

08:32.680 --> 08:33.981
HOW DOES A DOCTOR
BELIEVE THIS CRAP?

08:34.014 --> 08:36.717
HE'S AN AIDS DENIER,
PART OF A MISGUIDED MINORITY

08:36.750 --> 08:38.652
WHO BELIEVES THAT HIV
DOESN'T CAUSE AIDS,

08:38.686 --> 08:40.754
AND THAT AIDS ITSELF
DOESN'T EXIST.

08:40.788 --> 08:43.757
WELL, HIS DENIAL NEARLY KILLED
ANTONIA SUAREZ.

08:43.791 --> 08:46.259
WHAT'S HER PROGNOSIS?
SHE'S DOING OKAY.

08:46.293 --> 08:47.728
BUT DR. MASSEY
DOESN'T THINK

08:47.761 --> 08:48.829
SHE'S GONNA MAKE IT
TO HIGH SCHOOL.

08:48.862 --> 08:50.964
CHANCES ARE SHE'S NOT
HIS FIRST MEDICAL SCREW-UP.

08:50.998 --> 08:52.933
IT'S TIME WE PUT
DR. DO-NOTHING OUT OF BUSINESS.

08:52.966 --> 08:54.568
WELL,
HUTTON'S NOT TALKING,

08:54.602 --> 08:56.336
AND PRIVILEGE
PUTS HIS FILES OFF LIMITS,

08:56.369 --> 08:58.706
SO HOW ARE WE GONNA FIND
THESE PATIENTS?

08:58.739 --> 09:02.876
I'LL CALL SOME REPORTER FRIENDS,
USE THE MEDIA TO SMOKE HIM OUT.

09:02.910 --> 09:05.345
(Greylek)
THIS POOR LITTLE BABY
IS IN STABLE CONDITION

09:05.378 --> 09:07.581
AT A LOCAL HOSPITAL.

09:07.615 --> 09:08.782
WE ARE APPEALING TO THE PUBLIC

09:08.816 --> 09:10.083
TO HELP US FIND HER FATHER.

09:10.117 --> 09:12.753
IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION,
PLEASE CALL

09:12.786 --> 09:16.824
SVU'S CONFIDENTIAL TIP LINE
AT THE NUMBER ON YOUR SCREEN.

09:16.857 --> 09:18.726
MISS GREYLEK, WHY IS THE BABY
IN THE HOSPITAL?

09:18.759 --> 09:20.661
SHE WAS RUSHED THERE
AFTER NEARLY DYING

09:20.694 --> 09:22.930
FROM RECKLESS TREATMENT
FOR A LIFE-THREATENING ILLNESS.

09:22.963 --> 09:24.732
WHO'S RESPONSIBLE
FOR THIS RECKLESS TREATMENT?

09:24.765 --> 09:26.066
A LICENSED PHYSICIAN.

09:26.099 --> 09:28.101
(woman)
WHAT'S HIS NAME?
DR. GIDEON HUTTON.

09:28.135 --> 09:29.803
ARE YOU INVESTIGATING HIM?

09:29.837 --> 09:30.904
NOT AT THIS TIME.

09:30.938 --> 09:33.807
BUT WE ENCOURAGE THE PUBLIC
TO PLEASE COME FORWARD

09:33.841 --> 09:34.808
WITH ANY INFORMATION

09:34.842 --> 09:37.277
REGARDING ANY
OF DR. HUTTON'S OTHER PATIENTS.

09:37.310 --> 09:38.746
(Hutton)
THIS LIBELOUS TRASH

09:38.779 --> 09:40.714
HAS BEEN RUNNING
ALL AFTERNOON!

09:40.748 --> 09:42.315
I AM DONE WITH YOU PEOPLE

09:42.349 --> 09:43.851
PROPAGATING LIES
ABOUT MY CLIENT.

09:43.884 --> 09:46.720
MISS GREYLEK IS DOING
THE PROPAGATING, COUNSELOR.

09:46.754 --> 09:48.956
YOUR BEEF
IS WITH THE D.A.'S OFFICE.

09:48.989 --> 09:50.223
NO,
IT'S WITH YOUR DETECTIVES.

09:50.257 --> 09:52.159
THEY INTERROGATED
DR. HUTTON IN HIS OFFICE

09:52.192 --> 09:53.160
WITHOUT ME PRESENT.

09:53.193 --> 09:54.762
THAT WAS
A FRIENDLY CHAT.

09:54.795 --> 09:56.864
WHEN WE INTERROGATE DR. HUTTON,
HE'LL KNOW IT.

09:56.897 --> 09:58.932
YOU'RE SCARING
MY PATIENTS.

09:58.966 --> 10:00.100
THEY SHOULD BE SCARED.

10:00.133 --> 10:01.635
THAT'S IT.
LET'S GO, GIDEON.

10:01.669 --> 10:04.171
WE GET A PUBLIC APOLOGY
WITHIN 24 HOURS,

10:04.204 --> 10:06.139
OR YOU'RE AT THE WRONG END

10:06.173 --> 10:07.775
OF A VERY EXPENSIVE LAWSUIT.

10:09.442 --> 10:11.812
I GUESS A HUG'S
OUT OF THE QUESTION?

10:11.845 --> 10:13.781
WHAT DID YOU GET
FROM THE TIP LINE?

10:13.814 --> 10:15.148
A COUPLE HUNDRED PEOPLE
SAY THAT HUTTON

10:15.182 --> 10:17.284
IS THE GREATEST DOCTOR
SINCE ALBERT SCHWEITZER.

10:17.317 --> 10:19.252
TALK TO ANYONE WHO'S
NOT A MEMBER OF THE FAN CLUB?

10:19.286 --> 10:21.021
ONE ANONYMOUS CALLER
SAYS THAT HUTTON

10:21.054 --> 10:23.190
IS TREATING A GIRL
NAMED LISA ROSS WITH HIV,

10:23.223 --> 10:25.358
BUT HE'S
NOT DOING ANYTHING.

10:27.895 --> 10:30.931
[knocking]

10:30.964 --> 10:32.966
CAN I HELP YOU?

10:33.000 --> 10:34.935
YEAH, POLICE.
LISA ROSS LIVE HERE?

10:34.968 --> 10:36.236
SHE USED TO.

10:36.269 --> 10:37.738
DID SHE MOVE?

10:39.172 --> 10:42.209
NO.
MY SISTER'S DEAD.

10:49.850 --> 10:51.351
THAT'S LISA.

10:51.384 --> 10:54.788
THAT WAS TWO MONTHS AGO.

10:54.822 --> 10:57.958
IT WAS JUST BEFORE
SHE DIED.

10:57.991 --> 11:00.828
WE'RE SO SORRY
FOR YOUR LOSS.

11:00.861 --> 11:02.896
THANK YOU.
MOM.

11:02.930 --> 11:05.866
TOMMY, HOMEWORK NOW.

11:08.836 --> 11:10.303
HOW DID YOUR DAUGHTER
DIE?

11:12.039 --> 11:13.907
AN ALLERGIC REACTION
TO PENICILLIN.

11:13.941 --> 11:16.810
SHE HAD A COUGH
AND A FEVER.

11:16.844 --> 11:18.779
I TOOK HER
TO THE FAMILY DOCTOR.

11:18.812 --> 11:19.947
GIDEON HUTTON?

11:19.980 --> 11:21.815
YEAH.

11:21.849 --> 11:23.951
HE PRESCRIBED AMOXICILLIN,

11:23.984 --> 11:27.855
I GAVE HER A DOSE OF IT.

11:27.888 --> 11:30.891
AND ALL OF A SUDDEN...

11:30.924 --> 11:33.026
SHE WAS HAVING TROUBLE
BREATHING,

11:33.060 --> 11:36.129
SO I RUSHED HER BACK.

11:36.163 --> 11:37.430
HE GAVE HER A SHOT
OF ADRENALINE.

11:37.464 --> 11:39.332
HE EVEN SHOCKED HER HEART,

11:39.366 --> 11:41.835
BUT IT WAS TOO LATE.

11:41.869 --> 11:44.471
SHE WAS GONE.

11:44.504 --> 11:45.773
DR. HUTTON DIDN'T KNOW

11:45.806 --> 11:47.941
THAT SHE WAS ALLERGIC
TO PENICILLIN?

11:47.975 --> 11:49.877
I DIDN'T KNOW
SHE WAS ALLERGIC TO PENICILLIN.

11:49.910 --> 11:52.012
SHE'D NEVER TAKEN
AN ANTIBIOTIC BEFORE.

11:52.045 --> 11:55.048
LISA WAS VERY HEALTHY.

11:55.082 --> 11:58.218
SHE WAS VERY HEALTHY
UNTIL SHE HAD THAT COLD.

11:58.251 --> 12:00.320
MISS ROSS,
WE RECEIVED AN ANONYMOUS CALL

12:00.353 --> 12:03.090
CLAIMING THAT LISA HAD HIV

12:03.123 --> 12:05.225
AND DR. HUTTON
WASN'T TREATING HER FOR IT.

12:05.258 --> 12:08.528
IT'S NOT HIS FAULT...
THAT SHE DIED.

12:08.561 --> 12:11.899
IT WAS...AN ACCIDENT.

12:11.932 --> 12:12.833
WELL, WE NEED TO BE SURE,

12:12.866 --> 12:14.768
SO WE'D LIKE TO ASK YOU
FOR YOUR PERMISSION

12:14.802 --> 12:16.103
TO SEE
HER MEDICAL RECORDS.

12:16.136 --> 12:20.140
[exhales]
GOD, MY HUSBAND DIED...

12:20.173 --> 12:22.509
BEFORE I FOUND OUT
I WAS PREGNANT WITH LISA,

12:22.542 --> 12:25.145
AND NOW I CAN BARELY...

12:25.178 --> 12:27.848
GET OUT OF BED IN THE MORNING
WITHOUT HER.

12:27.881 --> 12:30.784
JUST PLEASE, WOULD--

12:32.185 --> 12:34.988
LEAVE ME AND TOMMY ALONE.

12:36.456 --> 12:38.225
IF HUTTON MADE A MISTAKE,

12:38.258 --> 12:40.060
THE M.E. WOULD HAVE SENT
HER CASE TO YOU.

12:40.093 --> 12:42.796
LISA'S BODY NEVER MADE IT
TO THE M.E.

12:42.830 --> 12:45.999
HUTTON SIGNED
THE DEATH CERTIFICATE.

12:46.033 --> 12:47.835
THE M.E. IS SUPPOSED
TO INVESTIGATE

12:47.868 --> 12:49.536
EVERY SUDDEN DEATH
OF A CHILD IN THE CITY.

12:49.569 --> 12:51.371
UNLESS IT HAPPENS
IN A HOSPITAL

12:51.404 --> 12:52.873
OR IN A DOCTOR'S OFFICE

12:52.906 --> 12:56.009
WHERE LIFE-SAVING EFFORTS
ARE FULLY DOCUMENTED.

12:56.043 --> 12:57.344
WITHOUT AN AUTOPSY,

12:57.377 --> 12:58.879
WE DON'T EVEN KNOW IF LISA
WAS HIV POSITIVE.

12:58.912 --> 13:00.914
AND WE DON'T HAVE ENOUGH
TO CONVINCE A JUDGE

13:00.948 --> 13:02.115
TO SUBPOENA HER MEDICAL RECORDS.

13:02.149 --> 13:04.117
OKAY.
SO WHAT DO WE NEED?

13:04.151 --> 13:07.320
YOUR ANONYMOUS TIPSTER.

13:09.589 --> 13:12.059
BE A LOT EASIER
TO FIND YOUR GUY

13:12.092 --> 13:13.827
IF WE COULD TRACE
OUR TIP LINES.

13:13.861 --> 13:15.028
AS SOON AS THE WORD
GOT OUT,

13:15.062 --> 13:16.964
WE'D NEVER GET
ANOTHER TIP.

13:16.997 --> 13:18.866
MUNCH GET ANYTHING
ON SUSAN?

13:18.899 --> 13:20.868
HE JUST EMAILED ME
SOME FILES.

13:20.901 --> 13:22.169
SHE TAUGHT ENGLISH

13:22.202 --> 13:23.871
AT A PRIVATE SCHOOL
IN CONNECTICUT

13:23.904 --> 13:24.872
UP UNTIL THREE YEARS AGO,

13:24.905 --> 13:27.207
THEN OUT OF THE BLUE,
SHE'S A STAY-AT-HOME MOM

13:27.240 --> 13:29.476
WITH A MANHATTAN CONDO

13:29.509 --> 13:32.379
AND A BIG, FAT BANK ACCOUNT.

13:32.412 --> 13:33.646
(Morales)
OKAY, HERE'S YOUR
ANONYMOUS CALLER.

13:33.680 --> 13:37.918
(Munch)
SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT.
CONFIDENTIAL TIP LINE.

13:37.951 --> 13:40.287
(man)
I SAW THAT NEWS PIECE
ABOUT DR. HUTTON.

13:40.320 --> 13:43.356
HE TAKES CARE OF A LITTLE GIRL
NAMED LISA ROSS.

13:43.390 --> 13:46.994
SHE HAS HIV, AND HE IS NOT
DOING ANYTHING TO HELP HER.

13:47.027 --> 13:49.129
(Munch)
DO YOU KNOW WHERE
THIS GIRL LIVES?

13:49.162 --> 13:51.464
(man)
602 EAST 73RD STREET.

13:51.498 --> 13:52.465
[indistinct sound,
dial tone]

13:52.499 --> 13:54.001
(Munch)
SIR?

13:54.034 --> 13:54.935
I HEARD A NOISE
JUST BEFORE HE HUNG UP.

13:54.968 --> 13:58.105
I HEARD IT TOO.
CAN YOU ISOLATE THAT SOUND?

13:58.138 --> 14:00.007
HOW'S THIS?

14:00.040 --> 14:00.941
[bell ringing]

14:00.974 --> 14:03.343
IT'S A BELL.
LIKE AT A SCHOOL.

14:03.376 --> 14:05.645
SUSAN ROSS WAS A TEACHER.

14:05.678 --> 14:07.614
MAYBE ONE OF HER COLLEAGUES
RATTED HER OUT.

14:07.647 --> 14:10.117
(Stabler)
COULD BE THE SAME ONE
WHO COSIGNED HER CAR LOAN.

14:10.150 --> 14:13.086
JACK LUFTON.
TEACHES CHEMISTRY.

14:15.388 --> 14:17.991
(Jack)
YEAH, I CALLED YOUR TIP LINE.

14:18.025 --> 14:20.127
(Benson)
YOU DIDN'T KNOW
LISA WAS DEAD.

14:20.160 --> 14:23.030
NO.
BUT I'M NOT SURPRISED.

14:23.063 --> 14:25.465
SUSAN AND I WENT OUT
FOR ABOUT A YEAR AND A HALF

14:25.498 --> 14:27.167
AFTER LISA WAS BORN.

14:27.200 --> 14:30.303
I WAS MONOGAMOUS
THE WHOLE TIME.

14:30.337 --> 14:32.405
BUT THEN I CAME UP
HIV POSITIVE

14:32.439 --> 14:34.441
ON SOME INSURANCE PHYSICAL.

14:36.343 --> 14:37.477
YOU TELL SUSAN?

14:37.510 --> 14:39.446
TELL HER?
I WENT NUTS.

14:39.479 --> 14:41.414
YOU KNOW WHAT SHE SAID?

14:41.448 --> 14:44.551
"WHAT'S THE BIG DEAL?
HIV DOESN'T MAKE YOU SICK."

14:44.584 --> 14:46.486
SHE KNEW SHE HAD HIV.

14:46.519 --> 14:48.455
SHE, AND HER HUSBAND ED,
AND TOMMY

14:48.488 --> 14:50.924
WENT ON SAFARI IN KENYA
BACK IN '03.

14:50.958 --> 14:53.093
THEIR JEEP FLIPPED OVER.

14:53.126 --> 14:54.928
ED WAS KILLED.

14:54.962 --> 14:56.029
TOMMY WAS FINE,

14:56.063 --> 14:59.032
BUT THE BLOOD TRANSFUSION
THAT SAVED SUSAN'S LIFE

14:59.066 --> 15:00.500
INFECTED HER.

15:00.533 --> 15:02.435
AND THEN SHE INFECTED ME.

15:02.469 --> 15:04.704
HOW YOU DOING?

15:04.737 --> 15:07.607
I'M ON ARVs.
MY VIRAL LOAD IS NEAR ZERO.

15:07.640 --> 15:09.409
AND I FEEL GREAT.

15:09.442 --> 15:11.144
DID YOU TELL THE SCHOOL?
YEAH, RIGHT AWAY.

15:11.178 --> 15:12.579
AND THAT'S WHY SUSAN
GOT FIRED.

15:12.612 --> 15:17.117
AND THE ADMINISTRATION
DECIDED TO PAY HER SEVEN FIGURES

15:17.150 --> 15:18.518
SO SHE WOULDN'T SUE.

15:18.551 --> 15:20.320
WHY WAS SHE FIRED
AND NOT YOU?

15:20.353 --> 15:22.189
WELL, SHE THINKS HIV
IS HARMLESS.

15:22.222 --> 15:23.523
WHAT IF SHE CUTS HERSELF

15:23.556 --> 15:25.392
AND ONE OF HER STUDENTS
GETS EXPOSED?

15:25.425 --> 15:27.961
HELL, SHE DOESN'T EVEN TAKE
PRECAUTIONS WITH HER OWN KIDS.

15:27.995 --> 15:29.296
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

15:29.329 --> 15:32.165
SHE BREAST-FED LISA
FOR A YEAR AFTER SHE WAS BORN

15:32.199 --> 15:34.701
BECAUSE DR. HUTTON
TOLD HER IT WAS OKAY.

15:36.303 --> 15:38.271
2/3 OF THE WORLD'S
HIV POSITIVE KIDS

15:38.305 --> 15:42.042
GET INFECTED DURING PREGNANCY
OR AT BIRTH FROM THE MOTHER.

15:42.075 --> 15:44.177
THE REST ACQUIRE IT
DURING BREAST-FEEDING.

15:44.211 --> 15:47.114
OKAY, SO SUSAN COULD HAVE PASSED
THE VIRUS TO LISA

15:47.147 --> 15:48.215
EITHER WAY.

15:48.248 --> 15:49.016
IT'S A SHAME.

15:49.049 --> 15:51.218
HIV POSITIVE WOMEN
IN THIS COUNTRY

15:51.251 --> 15:53.586
HAVE A 98% CHANCE
OF HAVING A HEALTHY BABY.

15:53.620 --> 15:56.656
IF THEY TAKE ANTIRETROVIRALS
DURING PREGNANCY

15:56.689 --> 15:59.226
AND PUT THE CHILD ON MEDS
AFTER BIRTH.

15:59.259 --> 16:00.527
WHICH SUSAN
PROBABLY DIDN'T DO

16:00.560 --> 16:02.195
BECAUSE SHE THINKS
HIV IS HARMLESS.

16:02.229 --> 16:03.430
YEAH, SHE PUT LISA'S LIFE
IN DANGER

16:03.463 --> 16:05.198
BY BREAST-FEEDING HER

16:05.232 --> 16:07.200
AND BY WITHHOLDING MEDICATION
WHEN LISA GOT SICK.

16:07.234 --> 16:09.702
AND SINCE ANY REASONABLE PERSON
KNOWS HIV CAUSES AIDS,

16:09.736 --> 16:11.304
THAT'S CRIMINALLY
NEGLIGENT HOMICIDE.

16:11.338 --> 16:12.505
(Stabler)
OKAY, WELL,

16:12.539 --> 16:13.506
HUTTON IS
OUR REAL PROBLEM HERE.

16:13.540 --> 16:16.043
HOW DO WE STOP HIM
BEFORE SOMEONE ELSE DIES?

16:16.076 --> 16:17.510
IF HUTTON KNEW SUSAN
HAD HIV,

16:17.544 --> 16:20.513
HE HAD A LEGAL DUTY TO MAKE SURE
HER KIDS WERE TESTED.

16:20.547 --> 16:22.682
EVEN IF HE BELIEVES
THAT HIV DOESN'T CAUSE AIDS?

16:22.715 --> 16:24.451
DOCTORS HAVE TO OFFER PATIENTS

16:24.484 --> 16:26.653
TREATMENTS
THAT ARE PROVEN EFFECTIVE.

16:26.686 --> 16:28.621
IN LISA'S CASE,
AN HIV TEST

16:28.655 --> 16:32.359
AND ANTIRETROVIRALS
IF SHE TESTED POSITIVE.

16:32.392 --> 16:34.127
OKAY, BUT HOW DO WE PROVE
SHE DIED OF AIDS

16:34.161 --> 16:35.228
AND NOT AN ALLERGIC REACTION
TO PENICILLIN?

16:35.262 --> 16:38.465
WELL, WE HAVE MORE THAN ENOUGH
PROBABLE CAUSE NOW.

16:38.498 --> 16:40.200
I'LL SUBPOENA
HUTTON'S FILES.

16:40.233 --> 16:44.471
THERE'S ONLY ONE CONCLUSIVE WAY
TO FIND OUT WHAT KILLED LISA.

16:47.507 --> 16:51.811
[Warner, dictating]
BODY IS THAT OF AN EMBALMED
FOUR-YEAR-OLD CAUCASIAN FEMALE.

16:51.844 --> 16:55.082
DECEASED APPROXIMATELY
TWO MONTHS.

16:55.115 --> 16:57.384
INITIALLY DETERMINED
CAUSE OF DEATH

16:57.417 --> 16:59.452
HAS NOW BEEN CALLED
INTO QUESTION,

16:59.486 --> 17:04.324
REQUIRING EXHUMATION AND FULL
POST-MORTEM EXAMINATION.

17:04.357 --> 17:06.559
(Susan)
YOU DUG UP MY DAUGHTER?

17:06.593 --> 17:09.362
HOW COULD YOU DO
SUCH A HORRIBLE THING?

17:09.396 --> 17:11.398
HOW COULD YOU KILL HER?

17:11.431 --> 17:14.234
MY CLIENT HAD AN ABSOLUTE RIGHT
TO BREAST-FEED HER CHILD.

17:14.267 --> 17:16.169
BUT SHE DIDN'T HAVE THE RIGHT
TO INFECT HER WITH HIV

17:16.203 --> 17:17.570
AND TO WITHHOLD MEDICATION.

17:17.604 --> 17:20.173
I DID NOT HURT MY BABY.

17:20.207 --> 17:23.143
I LOVED LISA.

17:23.176 --> 17:26.713
I DID NOT MAKE HER SICK.

17:26.746 --> 17:30.183
THE SKIN SHOWS NO SIGN
OF ABUSE-RELATED TRAUMA.

17:30.217 --> 17:33.786
THERE ARE NEEDLES PUNCTURES
TO THE CHEST AND ARMS

17:33.820 --> 17:37.424
CONSISTENT WITH EFFORTS
TO RESUSCITATE.

17:37.457 --> 17:39.392
MY CLIENT DID EVERYTHING
HE COULD TO SAVE LISA.

17:39.426 --> 17:41.428
EVERYTHING BUT TREAT
THE TIME BOMB

17:41.461 --> 17:43.296
HE KNEW WAS TICKING
INSIDE HER.

17:43.330 --> 17:45.398
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU ARE TALKING ABOUT,

17:45.432 --> 17:46.699
AND NEITHER DO YOU.

17:46.733 --> 17:48.168
NO, THE ONLY THING
THAT WE DON'T KNOW

17:48.201 --> 17:50.170
IS WHETHER LISA
WAS YOUR FIRST MISTAKE.

17:50.203 --> 17:52.639
BUT YOU CAN BET YOUR ASS
SHE'S YOUR LAST.

17:52.672 --> 17:55.808
ALL ORGANS ARE PRESENT
AND IN THEIR PROPER POSITIONS.

17:55.842 --> 17:59.612
BOTH KIDNEY AND LIVER
APPEAR ENLARGED.

17:59.646 --> 18:02.882
AN ULCERATED LESION
ON THE UPPER LIP

18:02.915 --> 18:05.252
SUGGESTS A VIRAL INCLUSION.

18:05.285 --> 18:08.455
(Susan)
DR. HUTTON SAID
IT WAS A CANKER SORE.

18:08.488 --> 18:10.523
IT WOULD GO AWAY
BY ITSELF.

18:10.557 --> 18:13.493
SO YOU TOOK HER TO SEE HIM
BEFORE THE DAY SHE DIED.

18:13.526 --> 18:15.895
YES, WHEN SHE
FIRST STARTED COUGHING.

18:15.928 --> 18:19.199
BUT HE DIDN'T PRESCRIBE
ANTIBIOTICS

18:19.232 --> 18:21.834
UNTIL HER LAST VISIT.

18:21.868 --> 18:24.371
HOW LONG WAS LISA SICK?

18:24.404 --> 18:26.873
THREE WEEKS.
SHE HAD A HELL OF A COLD.

18:26.906 --> 18:29.176
NEVER THOUGHT
IT MIGHT BE MORE SERIOUS?

18:29.209 --> 18:30.443
NOT UNTIL

18:30.477 --> 18:32.312
MOM BROUGHT HER BACK
FOR THE LAST TIME

18:32.345 --> 18:33.713
WITH COUGH AND FEVER,

18:33.746 --> 18:35.282
FOR WHICH I PRESCRIBED
AMOXICILLIN.

18:35.315 --> 18:37.550
THAT'S IT.
NO BLOOD TEST, CHEST X-RAY...

18:37.584 --> 18:38.818
WHY SUBJECT HER TO NEEDLES

18:38.851 --> 18:41.521
AND AN UNNECESSARY DOSE
OF RADIATION?

18:41.554 --> 18:45.558
I LISTENED TO HER LUNGS.
THEY WERE CLEAR.

18:45.592 --> 18:47.227
PRE-AUTOPSY X-RAYS SHOW

18:47.260 --> 18:49.162
SIGNIFICANT CONGESTION
IN BOTH LUNGS.

18:49.196 --> 18:52.265
PATHOLOGY OF THE PARENCHYMA
OF THE LOWER LOBE

18:52.299 --> 18:55.335
SHOW WHITE, PATCHY,
FLUFFY MASSES.

18:55.368 --> 18:56.203
WHICH MEANS WHAT?

18:56.236 --> 18:57.904
LISA DIED
OF PNEUMOCYSTIS PNEUMONIA.

18:57.937 --> 19:00.707
I'VE NEVER SEEN IT IN ANYONE
OTHER THAN AN AIDS PATIENT.

19:00.740 --> 19:01.908
SO MANNER OF DEATH?

19:01.941 --> 19:03.510
I'M RULING IT A HOMICIDE.

19:07.914 --> 19:09.282
PLEASE STAND UP, SUSAN.

19:12.919 --> 19:14.321
YOU'RE ARRESTING ME?

19:14.354 --> 19:15.655
[handcuffs clink]

19:15.688 --> 19:17.190
FOR MURDERING
YOUR DAUGHTER.

19:17.224 --> 19:19.592
I DELIVERED THAT CHILD.
I DIDN'T MURDER HER!

19:19.626 --> 19:21.628
AND NEITHER DID HER MOTHER!
LISA WAS MURDERED?

19:21.661 --> 19:23.830
NO! DON'T BELIEVE THEM,
TOMMY!
COME ON.

19:23.863 --> 19:25.765
MOM!

19:25.798 --> 19:27.300
YOU CAN'T TAKE HER TO JAIL!

19:27.334 --> 19:29.802
TOMMY, STAY STRONG. DON'T GO
AGAINST YOUR CONSCIENCE.

19:29.836 --> 19:31.003
YOU KNOW THE TRUTH.

19:31.037 --> 19:34.341
SHE WOULD NEVER HURT LISA.
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS TO US?

19:34.374 --> 19:36.243
TOMMY!

19:37.544 --> 19:39.546
SHH. SHH.

19:43.716 --> 19:45.352
(Warner)
HIV ATTACKS THE LIFE-SAVING
T CELLS

19:45.385 --> 19:46.919
THAT FIGHT DISEASE.

19:46.953 --> 19:48.621
THE VIRUS GENETICALLY
MUTATES THE HOST CELL,

19:48.655 --> 19:51.691
TURNING IT
INTO AN HIV FACTORY,

19:51.724 --> 19:54.227
WHICH MAKES MORE COPIES
OF THE VIRUS.

19:54.261 --> 19:55.995
EVENTUALLY, HIV KILLS T-CELLS

19:56.028 --> 19:58.665
FASTER THAN THE BODY
CAN REPLENISH THEM,

19:58.698 --> 20:01.768
DESTROYING THE IMMUNE SYSTEM
AND CAUSING AIDS.

20:01.801 --> 20:03.536
DR. WARNER,
CAN YOU TELL THE JURY

20:03.570 --> 20:04.837
HOW WE KNOW THIS?

20:04.871 --> 20:07.307
(Warner)
HIV HAS BEEN ISOLATED,

20:07.340 --> 20:09.342
PHOTOGRAPHED, CULTURED,

20:09.376 --> 20:12.345
AND GROWN
OUTSIDE THE HUMAN BODY.

20:12.379 --> 20:15.348
ITS GENETIC STRUCTURE
IS FULLY DOCUMENTED,

20:15.382 --> 20:19.286
AND IT'S KILLED MORE THAN
25 MILLION PEOPLE SINCE 1981,

20:19.319 --> 20:21.588
INCLUDING LISA ROSS.

20:24.924 --> 20:27.727
THANK YOU, DOCTOR.

20:27.760 --> 20:29.396
TRUE OR FALSE, DOCTOR:

20:29.429 --> 20:31.464
EVERY DISEASE
ALLEGEDLY CAUSED BY AIDS

20:31.498 --> 20:34.367
CAN ALSO APPEAR IN PEOPLE
WHO DON'T HAVE HIV.

20:34.401 --> 20:35.935
TRUE.

20:35.968 --> 20:37.604
WAS THE HIV
IN LISA ROSS'S BLOOD?

20:37.637 --> 20:38.905
NO, BUT--

20:38.938 --> 20:41.541
THEN ISN'T IT POSSIBLE
THAT HER PCP PNEUMONIA

20:41.574 --> 20:43.743
WAS CAUSED BY SOMETHING
OTHER THAN HIV: YES OR NO?

20:43.776 --> 20:45.278
IT'S NOT THAT SIMPLE.

20:45.312 --> 20:46.646
DO YOU HAVE A HEARING PROBLEM,
DOCTOR?

20:46.679 --> 20:48.515
YOUR HONOR, IS SHE GONNA
LET HER FINISH A SENTENCE?

20:48.548 --> 20:50.283
(Judge Bradley)
MS. EMMETT, THAT'S ENOUGH.

20:50.317 --> 20:53.620
YOU MAY ANSWER THE QUESTION,
DR. WARNER.

20:53.653 --> 20:57.457
I DIDN'T FIND HIV
IN LISA'S BLOODSTREAM

20:57.490 --> 20:59.392
BECAUSE SHE'D BEEN EMBALMED.

20:59.426 --> 21:02.395
AND ANYTHING
COMPROMISING THE IMMUNE SYSTEM

21:02.429 --> 21:03.530
CAN CAUSE PCP PNEUMONIA.

21:03.563 --> 21:07.400
CANCER, MALNUTRITION,
POISONING FROM RADIATION,

21:07.434 --> 21:09.502
OR TOXIC CHEMICALS.

21:09.536 --> 21:11.471
FINDING NO EVIDENCE
OF THOSE CONDITIONS,

21:11.504 --> 21:13.606
I CONCLUDED LISA ROSS
DIED OF AIDS

21:13.640 --> 21:16.443
CAUSED BY UNTREATED HIV.

21:16.476 --> 21:19.546
AND DR. HUTTON
REFUSED TO TREAT IT.

21:19.579 --> 21:21.381
(Dr. Hutton)
IT'S NONSENSE.

21:21.414 --> 21:23.950
HIV COULDN'T POSSIBLY
CAUSE AIDS...

21:23.983 --> 21:27.454
BECAUSE HIV
IS A RETROVIRUS.

21:27.487 --> 21:29.422
OR AS WE SAY, AN RV.

21:29.456 --> 21:31.524
AS IN RECREATIONAL
VEHICLE?

21:31.558 --> 21:32.492
ACTUALLY,
THEY ARE SIMILAR.

21:32.525 --> 21:35.995
HUNDREDS OF RVs
CARRY PASSENGER ORGANISMS

21:36.028 --> 21:38.498
THROUGH OUR BODIES
EVERY DAY...

21:38.531 --> 21:40.500
HARMLESSLY SO.

21:40.533 --> 21:43.703
NO RV HAS BEEN PROVEN
TO KILL CELLS.

21:43.736 --> 21:46.005
THEN WHY DID
THE MEDICAL EXAMINER

21:46.038 --> 21:48.007
SHOW US HIV
DOING EXACTLY THAT?

21:48.040 --> 21:50.510
WELL, CARTOONS
HAVE ALWAYS BEEN USED

21:50.543 --> 21:51.711
TO SPREAD PROPAGANDA.

21:51.744 --> 21:53.546
PROPAGANDA?

21:53.580 --> 21:56.549
THAT AIDS IS THIS COUNTRY'S
BIGGEST HEALTH THREAT

21:56.583 --> 21:58.785
AND THAT WE'RE ALL AT RISK.

21:58.818 --> 22:00.520
WELL, IF THAT'S NOT TRUE,

22:00.553 --> 22:02.589
THEN WHY SCARE US INTO THINKING
THAT WE'RE IN DANGER?

22:02.622 --> 22:04.090
(Hutton)
BECAUSE FEAR MOTIVATES.

22:04.123 --> 22:06.459
HOW ELSE COULD
GOVERNMENT RESEARCHERS

22:06.493 --> 22:09.529
GET BILLIONS IN FUNDING
TO CURE A DISEASE

22:09.562 --> 22:13.065
THAT KILLS MOSTLY
DRUG ADDICTS AND GAYS?

22:13.099 --> 22:16.569
DR. HUTTON,
WHAT DOES CAUSE AIDS?

22:16.603 --> 22:19.506
THOSE DISEASES,
INCORRECTLY ATTRIBUTED TO AIDS,

22:19.539 --> 22:21.441
ARE CAUSED BY BLOOD TOXICITY

22:21.474 --> 22:24.511
FROM REPEATED
RECREATIONAL DRUG USE,

22:24.544 --> 22:26.879
MALNUTRITION,

22:26.913 --> 22:29.015
AND ANTI-HIV MEDICATIONS.

22:29.048 --> 22:30.550
NO FURTHER QUESTIONS.

22:30.583 --> 22:31.784
DOCTOR, HAVE YOU

22:31.818 --> 22:35.655
EVER DONE ANY RESEARCH
ON HIV OR AIDS?

22:35.688 --> 22:37.524
NO.

22:37.557 --> 22:39.559
PUBLISHED ANY PAPERS
OR ARTICLES IN MEDICAL JOURNALS?

22:39.592 --> 22:42.895
MEDICAL JOURNALS ARE INTERESTED
IN THE STATUS QUO,

22:42.929 --> 22:45.432
NOT DISSENTING OPINIONS.

22:45.465 --> 22:47.634
SO YOU HAVE NO HARD EVIDENCE

22:47.667 --> 22:49.969
TO BACK UP
ANY OF YOUR ACCUSATIONS?

22:50.002 --> 22:51.871
OH, THERE'S PLENTY
OF EVIDENCE,

22:51.904 --> 22:54.474
COLLECTED FROM SOME OF
THE GREATEST SCIENTIFIC MINDS

22:54.507 --> 22:55.708
IN THE WORLD.

22:55.742 --> 22:59.646
YOU MEAN LIKE
THE SAN FRANCISCO BIOLOGIST

22:59.679 --> 23:02.815
WHO'S BECOME A PARIAH
IN THE SCIENTIFIC COMMUNITY?

23:02.849 --> 23:05.452
OR THE SOUTH AFRICAN
HEALTH MINISTER

23:05.485 --> 23:07.854
WHO ADVISED PEOPLE
WITH HIV

23:07.887 --> 23:10.590
TO EAT GARLIC AND BEET ROOT?

23:10.623 --> 23:12.559
YOU ARE MISSING
THE POINT.

23:12.592 --> 23:14.627
THERE ARE MILLIONS OF PEOPLE
BEING WRONGLY TREATED,

23:14.661 --> 23:15.895
WRONGLY DIAGNOSED.

23:15.928 --> 23:18.531
LIKE YOU MISDIAGNOSED
LISA ROSS.

23:18.565 --> 23:21.601
SHE DIED OF AN ALLERGIC REACTION
TO ANTIBIOTICS.

23:21.634 --> 23:24.704
NO.
SHE DIED OF AIDS.

23:24.737 --> 23:26.539
ACCORDING
TO YOUR PET MEDICAL EXAMINER,

23:26.573 --> 23:28.908
AND WE ALL KNOW
WHAT BIAS SHE HAS.

23:28.941 --> 23:30.577
COME ON, ASK HER

23:30.610 --> 23:31.978
HOW MANY OF HER FRIENDS
OR FAMILY MEMBERS

23:32.011 --> 23:33.613
HAVE DIED OF AIDS,

23:33.646 --> 23:34.981
EITHER HERE OR IN AFRICA?

23:35.014 --> 23:36.749
BECAUSE SHE'S BLACK?

23:36.783 --> 23:38.918
HOW DARE YOU!

23:38.951 --> 23:40.787
SHE HAS AN AGENDA.

23:40.820 --> 23:43.490
SHE'S JUST LIKE THE REST
OF THEM,

23:43.523 --> 23:45.492
THE DOCTORS THAT PERFORM
UNNECESSARY PROCEDURES

23:45.525 --> 23:47.460
JUST TO PAD THEIR WALLETS.
THAT'S ENOUGH, DOCTOR.

23:47.494 --> 23:49.829
THE DRUG COMPANIES WHO
KNOWINGLY PUT FLAWED MEDICINES

23:49.862 --> 23:52.565
ON THE MARKET
THAT CAN HURT OR KILL.

23:52.599 --> 23:54.934
DON'T LET THEM FOOL YOU,
TELL THEM THEY CANNOT

23:54.967 --> 23:57.036
YOUR HONOR...
KEEP GETTING AWAY
WITH THEIR LIES!

23:57.069 --> 24:00.740
LAST TIME, DOCTOR,
OR YOU'RE IN CONTEMPT.

24:00.773 --> 24:02.174
I'M THROUGH.

24:02.208 --> 24:05.978
(Judge Bradley)
WE WILL RECESS FOR LUNCH.

24:06.012 --> 24:07.246
CITY HEALTH DEPARTMENT
STUDY

24:07.279 --> 24:10.683
SAYS NEW YORKERS CONTRACT HIV
THREE TIMES THE NATIONAL RATE.

24:10.717 --> 24:12.485
THAT A LIE TOO?
WAKE UP, DOCTOR.

24:12.519 --> 24:15.555
WE HAVE IMMUNIZED PEOPLE
AGAINST EVERY VIRAL DISEASE

24:15.588 --> 24:16.523
FOR TWO CENTURIES.

24:16.556 --> 24:19.892
WE KNOW THAT PEOPLE PRODUCE
ANTIBODIES TO HIV.

24:19.926 --> 24:23.062
SO WHY IS THERE
NO ANTI-AIDS VACCINE,

24:23.095 --> 24:25.998
AND WHY HASN'T ONE AIDS PATIENT
EVER BEEN CURED?

24:26.032 --> 24:28.668
YOU SON OF A BITCH.
WE ALL WANT A CURE FOR AIDS.

24:28.701 --> 24:30.803
YOU'RE KILLING PEOPLE
WITH YOUR OUTRAGEOUS BELIEFS.

24:30.837 --> 24:32.872
MY BELIEFS
ARE SCIENTIFIC FACT.

24:32.905 --> 24:34.073
THEY'RE JUNK SCIENCE.

24:34.106 --> 24:36.609
YOU'RE A MURDERER
AND A FALSE PROPHET.

24:36.643 --> 24:39.712
THAT'S WHAT THEY CALLED
JESUS CHRIST.

24:43.550 --> 24:46.586
HOPE THE JURY DOESN'T THINK
HE'S THE SON OF GOD.

24:46.619 --> 24:48.755
JURORS LOVE
CONSPIRACY THEORIES.

24:48.788 --> 24:50.657
I'M AFRAID THEY MIGHT BUY
THE GARBAGE

24:50.690 --> 24:52.625
DR. STRANGELOVE'S SELLING.

24:52.659 --> 24:55.828
IT WE LOSE THIS CASE,
IT GIVES HIM CREDIBILITY,

24:55.862 --> 24:58.030
AND MORE PEOPLE WILL DIE.

25:01.701 --> 25:05.271
(Susan)
I FOUND OUT I HAD HIV
WHEN I WAS PREGNANT WITH LISA.

25:05.304 --> 25:08.608
I THOUGHT MY LIFE WAS OVER.

25:08.641 --> 25:12.078
DID YOUR DOCTORS
PUT YOU ON ANTIRETROVIRALS?

25:12.111 --> 25:13.279
YES.

25:13.312 --> 25:17.717
I'VE NEVER BEEN SICKER
IN MY LIFE.

25:17.750 --> 25:20.119
THEN A FRIEND RECOMMENDED
DR. HUTTON.

25:20.152 --> 25:21.554
WHAT DID HE DO
DIFFERENTLY?

25:21.588 --> 25:25.091
TOOK ME OFF
THE MEDICATION.

25:25.124 --> 25:27.960
DR. HUTTON SAVED MY LIFE.

25:29.696 --> 25:30.897
YOUR WITNESS.

25:34.701 --> 25:37.737
SO YOU BELIEVE
DR. HUTTON'S GOSPEL.

25:37.770 --> 25:39.739
YES. I DO.

25:39.772 --> 25:42.775
I'M LIVING PROOF
HE'S RIGHT.

25:42.809 --> 25:45.344
AND YOU DON'T THINK LISA'S DEATH
IS PROOF HE'S WRONG?

25:45.377 --> 25:47.747
LISA'S DEATH
WAS A TRAGIC ACCIDENT.

25:47.780 --> 25:49.248
OH, IT WAS TRAGIC.

25:49.281 --> 25:52.251
BUT IT WAS HARDLY
AN ACCIDENT.

25:53.753 --> 25:58.224
DID DR. HUTTON TELL YOU
NOT TO TEST LISA FOR HIV?

25:59.992 --> 26:01.227
NO.

26:01.260 --> 26:03.896
DID DR. HUTTON SUGGEST
SHE TAKE ARVs?

26:03.930 --> 26:06.232
ARVs ALMOST KILLED ME.

26:06.265 --> 26:09.201
I WAS NOT ABOUT TO GIVE THEM
TO MY LITTLE GIRL.

26:09.235 --> 26:12.304
RIGHT.

26:12.338 --> 26:14.907
DO YOU KNOW ANY
OF THESE PEOPLE?

26:17.243 --> 26:18.745
NO.

26:18.778 --> 26:19.979
NO, I'VE NEVER MET THEM.

26:20.012 --> 26:23.850
MAYBE YOU SHOULD.

26:23.883 --> 26:26.252
DONALD RAMIREZ
IS HIV POSITIVE.

26:26.285 --> 26:27.920
HE WAS ON DEATH'S DOOR

26:27.954 --> 26:30.322
20 YEARS AGO
WITH KAPOSI'S SARCOMA

26:30.356 --> 26:32.825
UNTIL ANTIRETROVIRALS
SAVED HIS LIFE.

26:32.859 --> 26:34.827
OBJECTION,
SHE'S TESTIFYING.

26:34.861 --> 26:37.697
15 YEARS AGO, ROBERTA NOLAN
TESTED HIV POSITIVE.

26:37.730 --> 26:39.198
YOUR HONOR?
MS. GREYLEK.

26:39.231 --> 26:41.067
(Greylek)
SHE'S STILL ALIVE
TODAY BECAUSE OF ARVs.

26:41.100 --> 26:42.201
LOOK AT THEM, SUSAN.

26:42.234 --> 26:44.370
THEY'RE ALIVE
AND LISA'S DEAD

26:44.403 --> 26:46.839
BECAUSE YOU
WITHHELD TREATMENT

26:46.873 --> 26:47.907
THAT WOULD HAVE SAVED
HER LIFE.

26:47.940 --> 26:49.742
(Hunter)
YOUR HONOR!

26:49.776 --> 26:51.343
(Judge Bradley)
MS. GREYLEK.

26:51.377 --> 26:52.344
[pounds gavel]

26:52.378 --> 26:53.612
SHE'S HAVING A SEIZURE!

26:54.847 --> 26:56.215
LET ME GO.
I AM HER DOCTOR.

26:59.251 --> 27:01.821
SOMEBODY CALL AN AMBULANCE.

27:09.829 --> 27:13.733
OH, WHERE AM I?

27:13.766 --> 27:18.204
YOU'RE IN MERCY HOSPITAL,
SUSAN.

27:18.237 --> 27:21.741
YOU COLLAPSED.

27:24.844 --> 27:27.246
WHAT'S WRONG WITH ME?

27:27.279 --> 27:32.218
YOU HAVE TOXOPLASMOSIS.

27:32.251 --> 27:35.454
IT'S A BRAIN DISEASE
THAT PEOPLE

27:35.487 --> 27:37.690
WITH AIDS GET.

27:40.927 --> 27:46.232
I HAD TERRIBLE MIGRAINES...

27:46.265 --> 27:49.668
AFTER LISA DIED.

27:52.839 --> 27:56.408
DOCTOR--
[exhales deeply]

27:56.442 --> 27:59.879
DR. HUTTON SAID
I WAS GRIEVING.

27:59.912 --> 28:02.782
THAT IT WOULD PASS.

28:02.815 --> 28:05.417
SUSAN, YOU KNEW
YOU HAD HIV.

28:07.854 --> 28:10.823
IT WAS ONLY A MATTER OF TIME
BEFORE YOU GOT SICK.

28:10.857 --> 28:13.860
I NEEDED TO BELIEVE HIM.

28:17.063 --> 28:19.365
THAT I WAS GONNA BE OKAY.

28:19.398 --> 28:23.770
WELL, DR. HUTTON WAS WRONG.

28:23.803 --> 28:25.905
HE WAS WRONG ABOUT LISA.

28:25.938 --> 28:30.409
AND HE WAS WRONG
ABOUT YOU.

28:30.442 --> 28:32.444
BUT HE'S THE DOCTOR.

28:37.449 --> 28:39.919
WHY WOULD HE--

28:39.952 --> 28:41.788
WHY WOULD HE LIE TO ME?

28:43.890 --> 28:47.259
SUSAN,

28:47.293 --> 28:50.296
BECAUSE IF HE ADMITS
THE TRUTH,

28:50.329 --> 28:53.966
THEN HE HAS TO TAKE
RESPONSIBILITY

28:54.000 --> 28:58.938
FOR WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOUR LITTLE GIRL.

28:58.971 --> 29:00.940
AND WHAT'S HAPPENING
TO YOU.

29:13.185 --> 29:15.521
IT'S MY FAULT LISA'S DEAD.

29:19.892 --> 29:22.094
[crying]
I KILLED MY DAUGHTER.

29:22.128 --> 29:25.097
BECAUSE DR. HUTTON
MISLED YOU.

29:25.131 --> 29:30.837
SO HELP ME STOP HIM
BEFORE ANOTHER PERSON DIES.

29:37.009 --> 29:39.145
LISA'S NOT
THE ONLY ONE.

29:41.113 --> 29:43.149
THE ONLY WHAT?

29:46.318 --> 29:49.355
CHILDREN WHO DIED.

29:49.388 --> 29:51.824
[electronic beeping]

29:51.858 --> 29:54.827
TOMMY!

29:56.062 --> 29:58.998
[flatline tone]

29:59.031 --> 30:00.833
AH, SUSAN?

30:00.867 --> 30:01.834
SUSAN!

30:01.868 --> 30:03.202
SHE'S CODING.

30:03.235 --> 30:04.971
ALICE!
RIGHT BEHIND YOU.

30:13.980 --> 30:14.981
WHERE'S MY MOM?

30:17.249 --> 30:18.550
[whispers]
I'M SORRY, TOMMY.

30:33.665 --> 30:37.036
I'M SORRY.

30:37.069 --> 30:39.071
I LOVE YOU.

30:43.542 --> 30:45.544
I LOVE YOU.

30:51.350 --> 30:53.285
SUSAN ROSS DIED
LAST NIGHT OF AIDS.

30:53.319 --> 30:54.586
NO, SHE DIDN'T.

30:54.620 --> 30:56.122
I WAS WITH HER.

30:56.155 --> 30:58.390
MY CLIENT WAS REFERRING
TO HER CAUSE OF DEATH.

30:58.424 --> 31:00.259
END-STAGE TOXOPLASMOSIS.

31:00.292 --> 31:02.461
(Greylek)
WHICH THE M.E. SAYS
IS AN AIDS-RELATED DISEASE.

31:02.494 --> 31:04.396
BUT WE KNOW
YOU'LL DENY IT.

31:04.430 --> 31:06.232
THEN WHY DRAG US
IN HERE?

31:06.265 --> 31:08.234
BECAUSE SUSAN MADE
A DYING DECLARATION.

31:08.267 --> 31:10.236
SHE TOLD ME THAT LISA WASN'T
THE ONLY CHILD YOU KILLED.

31:10.269 --> 31:12.404
THE DEMENTED RAMBLINGS
OF A WOMAN WHOSE BRAIN

31:12.438 --> 31:13.539
WAS SWISS CHEESE.

31:13.572 --> 31:15.007
THEY WON'T BE ADMISSIBLE.

31:15.041 --> 31:16.408
YEAH, BUT THE RECORDS
FROM THE PHARMACY

31:16.442 --> 31:18.344
IN YOUR BUILDING WILL BE.

31:18.377 --> 31:19.378
WE SUBPOENAED EVERY ONE
OF YOUR PRESCRIPTIONS FILLED

31:19.411 --> 31:20.646
AT THAT DRUG STORE.

31:20.679 --> 31:22.148
WE BUILT A LIST
OF YOUR PATIENTS

31:22.181 --> 31:25.151
AND FOUND THE GRIEVING PARENTS
OF TWO CHILDREN

31:25.184 --> 31:26.618
WITH HIV
YOU WILLFULLY MISDIAGNOSED.

31:26.652 --> 31:29.488
RIGHT NOW WE'RE EXHUMING
THEIR BODIES.

31:29.521 --> 31:32.524
AUTOPSIES WILL PROVE THEY DIED
OF UNTREATED HIV.

31:32.558 --> 31:35.361
THREE DEAD KIDS.

31:35.394 --> 31:38.364
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

31:38.397 --> 31:40.499
HE PLEADS GUILTY TO
CRIMINALLY NEGLIGENT HOMICIDE,

31:40.532 --> 31:43.269
SURRENDERS HIS MEDICAL LICENSE
AND PATIENT RECORDS.

31:43.302 --> 31:47.339
I RECOMMEND FIVE YEARS.

31:47.373 --> 31:49.208
I'M NOT GONNA MAKE
ANY DEALS.

31:49.241 --> 31:50.209
TAKE IT, GIDEON.

31:50.242 --> 31:52.044
IT'S OVER.

31:57.183 --> 32:01.988
OKAY, BUT YOU'RE
NOT GONNA SILENCE ME.

32:02.021 --> 32:05.091
I WILL SPEAK THE TRUTH
FROM MY PRISON CELL.

32:05.124 --> 32:09.595
AND PEOPLE WILL LISTEN.

32:09.628 --> 32:11.297
HERE'S ANOTHER ONE.

32:11.330 --> 32:13.599
JANET HOOPER, 45,
MOTHER OF THREE.

32:13.632 --> 32:16.468
DIED OF BURKETT'S LYMPHOMA,
WHICH HUTTON TOLD HER

32:16.502 --> 32:19.705
WAS CAUSED BY HER EXPOSURE
TO TOXINS, NOT AIDS.

32:19.738 --> 32:23.442
HOW MANY
ARE WE UP TO?

32:23.475 --> 32:25.511
SEVEN FAMILIES
WE HAVE TO NOTIFY.

32:31.317 --> 32:32.284
OH, NO.

32:32.318 --> 32:33.452
WHAT DO YOU GOT?

32:33.485 --> 32:37.956
IT'S THE LAB REPORT
ON SUSAN'S FILE.

32:39.358 --> 32:41.327
[clears throat]

32:41.360 --> 32:46.498
SUSAN WAS HIV POSITIVE
IN 1993.

32:48.400 --> 32:51.470
TOMMY WAS BORN IN '94.

32:51.503 --> 32:54.106
SUSAN'S EX SAID SHE GOT INFECTED
RIGHT BEFORE LISA WAS BORN.

32:54.140 --> 32:56.408
THAT'S NINE YEARS
AFTER SHE HAD TOMMY.

32:56.442 --> 33:00.179
SHE LIED TO HER EX-BOYFRIEND
TO GET HIM OFF HER BACK.

33:00.212 --> 33:02.514
TOMMY COULD HAVE HIV.

33:02.548 --> 33:06.452
WE'VE GOTTA GET A COURT ORDER
AND HAVE HIM TESTED.

33:06.485 --> 33:08.120
GET AWAY FROM ME!
TOMMY, YOU'RE JUST GONNA--

33:08.154 --> 33:09.321
YOU CAN'T DO THIS TO ME!

33:09.355 --> 33:10.656
JUDGE SAYS WE CAN.
GET AWAY FROM ME!

33:10.689 --> 33:12.724
[grunts]

33:12.758 --> 33:13.725
I'M OKAY.

33:13.759 --> 33:15.194
HEY, GET OFF.

33:15.227 --> 33:17.196
GOOD KICK.
THAT HURT?

33:17.229 --> 33:18.464
[whispers]
YEAH, A LITTLE BIT, YEAH.

33:18.497 --> 33:20.066
OKAY, WE'RE GONNA HAVE
TO GET YOU AN X-RAY.

33:20.099 --> 33:21.467
TOMMY, YOU OKAY?
TAKE IT EASY.

33:23.135 --> 33:25.204
I DIDN'T LET THEM DO IT.
GOOD.

33:25.237 --> 33:26.705
I'M TAKING HIM
BACK TO THE SHELTER.

33:26.738 --> 33:28.507
WAIT A MINUTE, WAIT A MINUTE--
HE'S NOT YOUR CLIENT.

33:28.540 --> 33:29.475
HE IS NOW.

33:29.508 --> 33:31.410
STAYING STRONG HIRED ME
TO REPRESENT HIM.

33:31.443 --> 33:33.045
THAT'S A RESTRAINING ORDER
PREVENTING YOU

33:33.079 --> 33:34.246
FROM TESTING HIM FOR HIV.

33:34.280 --> 33:35.547
HE IS A MINOR
IN ACS CUSTODY.

33:35.581 --> 33:39.385
THAT GIVES THEM THE RIGHTS TO
MAKE MEDICAL DECISIONS FOR HIM.

33:39.418 --> 33:40.486
HE HAS THE RIGHT
TO REFUSE MEDICAL TREATMENT

33:40.519 --> 33:41.553
IF HE'S COMPETENT.

33:41.587 --> 33:45.257
COMPETENCE IN THIS CASE MEANS
TOMMY UNDERSTANDS

33:45.291 --> 33:47.293
THE CONSEQUENCES
OF HIS DECISION.

33:47.326 --> 33:48.794
WELL, OBVIOUSLY HE DOESN'T.

33:48.827 --> 33:50.729
SO WHAT'S THE NEXT MOVE?

33:50.762 --> 33:52.398
PUNT.

33:52.431 --> 33:53.699
TOMMY'S NOT CHARGED
WITH A CRIME,

33:53.732 --> 33:55.301
SO WE DON'T HAVE LEGAL STANDING
TO CHALLENGE

33:55.334 --> 33:56.302
THE RESTRAINING ORDER.

33:56.335 --> 33:58.737
THEN GET ACS TO FIGHT IT.
(Massey)
DETECTIVE?

33:58.770 --> 34:02.441
YOUR EIGHTH AND NINTH
RIGHT LATERAL RIBS ARE BROKEN.

34:02.474 --> 34:03.609
YEAH.

34:03.642 --> 34:05.177
BUSTED RIBS.
THIS IS PERFECT.

34:05.211 --> 34:06.778
EXCUSE ME?

34:06.812 --> 34:10.316
WE CAN PUT 'EM
TO GOOD USE.

34:10.349 --> 34:11.583
[school bell rings]

34:14.220 --> 34:16.288
MS. EMMETT SAID YOU CAN'T TALK
TO ME WITHOUT HER THERE.

34:16.322 --> 34:18.724
GOOD, I'M NOT HERE TO TALK.

34:18.757 --> 34:20.292
PUT YOUR HANDS
BEHIND YOUR BACK.

34:20.326 --> 34:22.361
WHY ARE YOU ARRESTING ME?

34:22.394 --> 34:24.263
ASSAULTING A POLICE OFFICER.

34:24.296 --> 34:26.565
YOU'RE JUST DOING THIS SO YOU
CAN MAKE ME HAVE THAT TEST.

34:26.598 --> 34:28.134
IF YOU'RE NOT GONNA HELP
YOURSELF,

34:28.167 --> 34:29.801
MAYBE A JUDGE WILL.

34:33.405 --> 34:35.741
(Emmett)
TOMMY, ARE YOU AWARE
THAT MOST PEOPLE BELIEVE

34:35.774 --> 34:37.476
THAT HIV CAUSES AIDS?

34:37.509 --> 34:40.279
YEAH, THEY TAUGHT US IT
IN SCHOOL.

34:40.312 --> 34:42.648
BUT YOUR MOTHER AND DR. HUTTON
TAUGHT YOU DIFFERENTLY.

34:42.681 --> 34:44.416
ISN'T THAT TRUE?

34:44.450 --> 34:46.118
THEY SAID HIV
DOESN'T CAUSE AIDS.

34:46.152 --> 34:47.119
AND YOU BELIEVE THEM?

34:47.153 --> 34:48.053
YES.

34:48.086 --> 34:49.855
BECAUSE YOUR MOTHER
AND DOCTOR TOLD YOU,

34:49.888 --> 34:51.623
OR BECAUSE YOU THINK
IT'S THE TRUTH?

34:51.657 --> 34:53.759
AFTER WE DISCUSSED AIDS
IN HEALTH CLASS,

34:53.792 --> 34:56.528
I TALKED TO MY MOM ABOUT IT.

34:56.562 --> 34:58.297
SHE EXPLAINED WHY THERE WAS NO
PROOF FOR WHAT THEY TAUGHT US,

34:58.330 --> 34:59.731
AND IT MADE SENSE.

34:59.765 --> 35:02.368
NOTHING FURTHER.

35:02.401 --> 35:05.704
WHAT DID SHE TELL YOU
THAT MADE SO MUCH SENSE?

35:05.737 --> 35:08.607
THAT HIV IS NOT THE KIND
OF VIRUS THAT CAN MAKE YOU SICK,

35:08.640 --> 35:11.577
THE DRUGS FOR AIDS CAN KILL YOU,
AND THAT THE DOCTORS

35:11.610 --> 35:14.646
AND THE DRUG COMPANIES WON'T
TELL THE TRUTH, SO THAT THEY

35:14.680 --> 35:16.648
CAN KEEP MAKING MONEY
OFF OF IT.

35:16.682 --> 35:18.817
SAME NONSENSE WE'VE HEARD
OVER AND OVER AGAIN

35:18.850 --> 35:22.488
RIGHT OUT
OF THE AIDS-DENIERS' PLAYBOOK.

35:22.521 --> 35:24.456
TOMMY, ARE YOU FAMILIAR
WITH THE HOLOCAUST?

35:24.490 --> 35:27.226
SURE, WHO ISN'T?

35:27.259 --> 35:29.228
DO YOU BELIEVE
IT ACTUALLY OCCURRED?

35:29.261 --> 35:30.562
OF COURSE.

35:30.596 --> 35:31.730
WHY WOULDN'T I?

35:31.763 --> 35:33.265
BECAUSE THERE ARE PEOPLE
WHO DON'T.

35:33.299 --> 35:36.402
DOES THAT SURPRISE YOU?

35:36.435 --> 35:38.304
YEAH.

35:38.337 --> 35:40.339
JUST BECAUSE THEY BELIEVE THAT
DOESN'T MAKE IT THE TRUTH.

35:40.372 --> 35:42.441
THEN WHY?

35:42.474 --> 35:45.911
SINCE WE KNOW HIV CAUSES AIDS,
WOULD YOU BELIEVE PEOPLE

35:45.944 --> 35:48.180
WHO SAY IT DOESN'T?

35:48.214 --> 35:50.282
MY MOM WOULDN'T LIE TO ME.

35:50.316 --> 35:51.750
SURE SHE WOULD.

35:51.783 --> 35:54.253
BECAUSE IF YOU DECIDED
TO GET TESTED FOR HIV

35:54.286 --> 35:55.587
AND TURNED UP POSITIVE,
IT WOULD SHATTER

35:55.621 --> 35:57.423
HER FANTASY WORLD.

35:57.456 --> 35:58.424
I FEEL FINE.

35:58.457 --> 35:59.491
I'M NOT SICK.

35:59.525 --> 36:00.926
NOW STOP TRYING TO SCARE ME.

36:00.959 --> 36:01.860
YOU SHOULD BE SCARED.

36:01.893 --> 36:04.463
YOUR MOTHER SOLD YOU A BILL
OF GOODS, TOMMY.

36:04.496 --> 36:06.965
SHE RISKED YOUR LIFE
TO FEED HER DENIAL.

36:06.998 --> 36:09.201
STOP SAYING BAD THINGS
ABOUT MY MOTHER.

36:09.235 --> 36:11.303
SHE WATCHED YOUR SISTER DIE,
AND NOW SHE'S DEAD

36:11.337 --> 36:12.638
BECAUSE SHE WOULDN'T FACE
THE TRUTH.

36:12.671 --> 36:13.705
YOUR HONOR--

36:13.739 --> 36:16.375
DO YOU HAVE TO BE DYING TOO
BEFORE YOU SEE HER LIES?

36:16.408 --> 36:17.776
PLEASE, STOP!

36:17.809 --> 36:19.845
PLEASE, STOP IT!

36:19.878 --> 36:20.846
YOUR HONOR.
(Judge Bradley)
MS. GREYLEK.

36:20.879 --> 36:23.615
NO FURTHER QUESTIONS.

36:31.657 --> 36:35.927
THE QUESTION
BEFORE US TODAY...

36:35.961 --> 36:37.829
IS WHEN DOES THE STATE
HAVE THE RIGHT TO FORCE SOMEONE

36:37.863 --> 36:39.731
TO RECEIVE
MEDICAL CARE?

36:39.765 --> 36:41.900
HAD THIS COURT KNOWN
ABOUT YOUR SISTER'S ILLNESS,

36:41.933 --> 36:43.969
I WOULD HAVE COMPELLED HER
TO BE TREATED

36:44.002 --> 36:45.837
BECAUSE SHE WAS
ONLY FOUR YEARS OLD.

36:45.871 --> 36:48.940
YOU, YOUNG MAN,
ARE A DIFFERENT STORY.

36:48.974 --> 36:52.678
ALTHOUGH YOU ARE A MINOR,
YOU ARE SUFFICIENTLY AWARE

36:52.711 --> 36:55.481
OF THE CONSEQUENCES
OF NOT BEING TESTED FOR HIV.

36:55.514 --> 37:00.352
I DISAGREE
WITH YOUR CHOICE.

37:00.386 --> 37:02.788
BUT TO TAKE IT AWAY
DEPRIVES YOU OF YOUR RIGHT

37:02.821 --> 37:05.457
TO MAKE DECISIONS
ABOUT YOUR OWN HEALTH.

37:05.491 --> 37:08.527
I AM THEREFORE UPHOLDING
THE RESTRAINING ORDER

37:08.560 --> 37:09.795
AND RULING IN FAVOR

37:09.828 --> 37:11.863
OF THE DEFENDANT.
[pounds gavel]

37:11.897 --> 37:12.864
YOUR HONOR,
WE MOVE THE DEFENDANT

37:12.898 --> 37:13.865
BE REMANDED WITHOUT BAIL.

37:13.899 --> 37:15.401
WHAT?

37:15.434 --> 37:16.402
HE ASSAULTED
A POLICE OFFICER

37:16.435 --> 37:17.469
AND HE'S A KNOWN FLIGHT RISK.

37:17.503 --> 37:18.770
THIS IS VINDICTIVE.

37:18.804 --> 37:20.572
ONE MOMENT, YOUR HONOR.

37:20.606 --> 37:22.040
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

37:22.073 --> 37:24.576
TREATING TOMMY LIKE THE ADULT
HE WANTS TO BE.

37:24.610 --> 37:26.612
HIS ONLY CRIME WAS BEING BORN
TO THE WRONG MOTHER.

37:26.645 --> 37:28.547
WE'RE NOT SENDING
A KID TO JAIL.

37:28.580 --> 37:29.548
YOU PRESSED THE CHARGES.

37:29.581 --> 37:32.551
BECAUSE I WANTED
TO FORCE TOMMY TO GET TESTED.

37:32.584 --> 37:34.320
LOOK, WE LOST.
IT'S OVER.

37:34.353 --> 37:35.887
CASE IS DONE.

37:39.658 --> 37:42.661
YOUR HONOR,
THE PEOPLE WITHDRAW THE MOTION

37:42.694 --> 37:44.796
AND DISMISS THE SOLE COUNT
OF ASSAULT

37:44.830 --> 37:45.964
IN THE SECOND DEGREE.

37:45.997 --> 37:47.833
(Judge Bradley)
MOTION WITHDRAWN.

37:47.866 --> 37:49.368
CHARGES ARE DISMISSED

37:49.401 --> 37:51.570
AND WE ARE ADJOURNED.
[pounds gavel]

37:54.540 --> 37:57.376
I HOPE YOU KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE DOING.

38:04.916 --> 38:07.319
THANKS.

38:07.353 --> 38:09.421
YEAH?

38:09.455 --> 38:10.956
YOU STILL OWE ME
FOR THE BUSTED RIBS.

38:10.989 --> 38:13.091
I'M NOT GETTING TESTED.

38:13.124 --> 38:16.995
I KNOW.

38:17.028 --> 38:19.064
JUST DO ME ONE FAVOR.

38:25.737 --> 38:27.539
WHY ARE WE HERE?

38:27.573 --> 38:28.574
I WANT YOU TO MEET SOMEONE

38:28.607 --> 38:30.742
THAT DR. MASSEY
INTRODUCED ME TO.

38:34.546 --> 38:35.681
HOW ARE YOU?

38:35.714 --> 38:37.749
[quietly]
I'M OKAY.

38:37.783 --> 38:38.850
I TOLD YOU
I'D COME BACK.

38:38.884 --> 38:40.852
ARE YOU UP
FOR DOING THIS?

38:40.886 --> 38:41.720
YEAH.

38:41.753 --> 38:45.391
TOMMY, I'D LIKE FOR YOU
TO MEET KYLE.

38:45.424 --> 38:46.725
HEY.

38:46.758 --> 38:48.394
HEY.

38:48.427 --> 38:49.628
YOU'RE NOT GONNA CHANGE
MY MIND

38:49.661 --> 38:51.397
JUST BECAUSE THE KID
HAS AIDS.

38:51.430 --> 38:52.931
(Kyle)
I DON'T HAVE AIDS.

38:52.964 --> 38:55.767
I HAVE BRAIN CANCER.

38:55.801 --> 38:58.770
I TOLD MY PARENTS
I DIDN'T FEEL WELL.

38:58.804 --> 39:02.040
BUT WE'RE CHRISTIAN SCIENTISTS,
SO WE DON'T BELIEVE IN DOCTORS

39:02.073 --> 39:03.575
OR MEDICINE.

39:03.609 --> 39:05.477
WHAT'D THEY
TELL YOU TO DO?

39:05.511 --> 39:07.979
PRAY.

39:08.013 --> 39:09.848
THEY SAID THAT THEY'D PRAY
FOR ME TOO,

39:09.881 --> 39:14.520
AND I KNEW I'D BE OKAY.

39:14.553 --> 39:18.790
BECAUSE I BELIEVED
LIKE THEY DID.

39:18.824 --> 39:19.825
THEN I WENT BLIND.

39:19.858 --> 39:21.727
YOU COULDN'T SEE?

39:21.760 --> 39:23.795
NO.

39:23.829 --> 39:24.730
ASKED MY FRIEND

39:24.763 --> 39:26.932
TO TAKE ME
TO THE HOSPITAL.

39:26.965 --> 39:29.000
AND THE DOCTORS...

39:29.034 --> 39:30.836
THEY GAVE ME CHEMO
AND RADIATION.

39:30.869 --> 39:33.104
AND I ALREADY GOT
MY SIGHT BACK.

39:33.138 --> 39:35.841
YOUR FOLKS
MUST HAVE BEEN HAPPY.

39:35.874 --> 39:37.876
NO.

39:37.909 --> 39:40.546
THEY WERE PISSED.

39:40.579 --> 39:44.716
THEY THOUGHT
I WAS DISSING GOD.

39:44.750 --> 39:46.785
WHAT DID YOU THINK?

39:46.818 --> 39:50.155
I JUST WANNA GET BETTER.

39:54.660 --> 39:56.695
WHAT ABOUT EVERYTHING
YOU BELIEVED IN?

39:59.230 --> 40:04.603
MY GRANDMA SAYS GOD CREATED
DOCTORS TOO, RIGHT?

40:04.636 --> 40:08.740
WHY WOULD HE GIVE US
ALL THESE CURES AND TREATMENTS

40:08.774 --> 40:13.912
FOR DISEASES IF HE
DIDN'T WANT US TO USE THEM?

40:29.895 --> 40:30.862
HE OKAY?

40:30.896 --> 40:32.831
HE WANTS TO TALK
TO YOU.

40:51.617 --> 40:53.485
YOU DON'T HAVE
TO TELL ME.

40:53.519 --> 40:56.154
I WANT TO.

41:02.027 --> 41:04.462
THE TEST CAME BACK
POSITIVE.

41:13.939 --> 41:15.774
I DON'T WANNA DIE.

41:15.807 --> 41:20.011
[whispers]
HEY.

41:20.045 --> 41:23.281
YOU'VE GOT YOUR WHOLE LIFE
AHEAD OF YOU.

